      *-----------------------------------------------
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *-----------------------------------------------
     C           P#CMD     PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@CMD 256
     C                     PARM           P@LEN  155
      *
     C           K#FCX     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           AWPRT1
     C                     KFLD           AWPRT2
     C                     KFLD           AWPRT3
     C           KEYTKR    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @@TK1
     C                     KFLD           @@TK2
     C                     KFLD           @@TK3
     C                     KFLD           @@TK4
